{
  "chapter": {
    "id": "web:genesis.10",
    "translationId": "web",
    "bookSlug": "genesis",
    "chapterNumber": 10,
    "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10",
    "summary": "Source text for Genesis 10 in World English Bible."
  },
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.1",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:1",
      "text": "Now this is the history of the generations of the sons of Noah and of Shem, Ham, and Japheth. Sons were born to them after the flood.",
      "paragraphStart": true
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.2",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:2",
      "text": "The sons of Japheth were: Gomer, Magog, Madai, Javan, Tubal, Meshech, and Tiras.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.3",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:3",
      "text": "The sons of Gomer were: Ashkenaz, Riphath, and Togarmah.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.4",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:4",
      "text": "The sons of Javan were: Elishah, Tarshish, Kittim, and Dodanim.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.5",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:5",
      "text": "Of these were the islands of the nations divided in their lands, everyone after his language, after their families, in their nations.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.6",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:6",
      "text": "The sons of Ham were: Cush, Mizraim, Put, and Canaan.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.7",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:7",
      "text": "The sons of Cush were: Seba, Havilah, Sabtah, Raamah, and Sabteca. The sons of Raamah were: Sheba and Dedan.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.8",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:8",
      "text": "Cush became the father of Nimrod. He began to be a mighty one in the earth.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.9",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:9",
      "text": "He was a mighty hunter before Yahweh. Therefore it is said, “like Nimrod, a mighty hunter before Yahweh”.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.10",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:10",
      "text": "The beginning of his kingdom was Babel, Erech, Accad, and Calneh, in the land of Shinar.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.11",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:11",
      "text": "Out of that land he went into Assyria, and built Nineveh, Rehoboth Ir, Calah,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.12",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:12",
      "text": "and Resen between Nineveh and the great city Calah.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.13",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 13,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:13",
      "text": "Mizraim became the father of Ludim, Anamim, Lehabim, Naphtuhim,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.14",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 14,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:14",
      "text": "Pathrusim, Casluhim (which the Philistines descended from), and Caphtorim.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.15",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 15,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:15",
      "text": "Canaan became the father of Sidon (his firstborn), Heth,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.16",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 16,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:16",
      "text": "the Jebusites, the Amorites, the Girgashites,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.17",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 17,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:17",
      "text": "the Hivites, the Arkites, the Sinites,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.18",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 18,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:18",
      "text": "the Arvadites, the Zemarites, and the Hamathites. Afterward the families of the Canaanites were spread abroad.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.19",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 19,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:19",
      "text": "The border of the Canaanites was from Sidon — as you go toward Gerar — to Gaza — as you go toward Sodom, Gomorrah, Admah, and Zeboiim — to Lasha.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.20",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 20,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:20",
      "text": "These are the sons of Ham, after their families, according to their languages, in their lands and their nations.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.21",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 21,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:21",
      "text": "Children were also born to Shem (the elder brother of Japheth), the father of all the children of Eber.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.22",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 22,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:22",
      "text": "The sons of Shem were: Elam, Asshur, Arpachshad, Lud, and Aram.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.23",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 23,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:23",
      "text": "The sons of Aram were: Uz, Hul, Gether, and Mash.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.24",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 24,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:24",
      "text": "Arpachshad became the father of Shelah. Shelah became the father of Eber.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.25",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 25,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:25",
      "text": "To Eber were born two sons. The name of the one was Peleg, for in his days the earth was divided. His brother’s name was Joktan.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.26",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 26,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:26",
      "text": "Joktan became the father of Almodad, Sheleph, Hazarmaveth, Jerah,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.27",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 27,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:27",
      "text": "Hadoram, Uzal, Diklah,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.28",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 28,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:28",
      "text": "Obal, Abimael, Sheba,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.29",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 29,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:29",
      "text": "Ophir, Havilah, and Jobab. All these were the sons of Joktan.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.30",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 30,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:30",
      "text": "Their dwelling extended from Mesha, as you go toward Sephar, the mountain of the east.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.31",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 31,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:31",
      "text": "These are the sons of Shem, by their families, according to their languages, lands, and nations.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:genesis.10.32",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 32,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:32",
      "text": "These are the families of the sons of Noah, by their generations, according to their nations. The nations divided from these in the earth after the flood.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    }
  ]
}
